161
00:08:35,873 --> 00:08:36,714
Xiaoqi,

162
00:08:36,954 --> 00:08:38,834
seven cups of milk tea
and seven pieces of cake.

163
00:08:39,913 --> 00:08:41,033
Fang Leng?

164
