172
00:09:13,354 --> 00:09:14,194
Good morning, Mr. Fang.

173
00:09:14,194 --> 00:09:14,793
Good morning.

174
00:09:15,393 --> 00:09:16,913
What is taking her so long?

175
00:09:35,714 --> 00:09:36,194
Xiao...

176
00:09:36,194 --> 00:09:36,913
Hello.

177
00:09:40,513 --> 00:09:41,354
