273
00:13:48,633 --> 00:13:49,994
Is she someone

274
00:13:49,994 --> 00:13:51,273
you can drive away

275
00:13:51,273 --> 00:13:52,354
as you wish?

276
00:13:52,354 --> 00:13:53,913
